      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que $I_n \\to 0$  lorsque $n\\to\\infty$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I_n \\to 0\\)</span> lorsque\n<span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\to\\infty\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "1b6792b6-2af3-4bab-a02d-b04415fdc58d",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$I_n+I_{n+2} = \\frac1{n+1}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(I_n+I_{n+2} = \\frac1{n+1}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "34905ac6-a7ff-423e-b021-78490762f212",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $I_n$ en fonction de~$n$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I_n\\)</span> en fonction\nde <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "04e5aea7-6993-410e-90eb-96f2ab031f59",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$I_{2k} = \\frac1{2k-1} - \\frac1{2k-3} + \\dots + \\frac{(-1)^{k-1}}1 + (-1)^k\\frac\\pi4$,\\par\n         $I_{2k+1} = \\frac1{2k} - \\frac1{2k-2} + \\dots + \\frac{(-1)^{k-1}}2 - (-1)^k\\ln\\sqrt2$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(I_{2k} = \\frac1{2k-1} - \\frac1{2k-3} +\n\\dots + \\frac{(-1)^{k-1}}1 + (-1)^k\\frac\\pi4\\)</span>,</p>\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(I_{2k+1} = \\frac1{2k} - \\frac1{2k-2} +\n\\dots + \\frac{(-1)^{k-1}}2 - (-1)^k\\ln\\sqrt2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "736999d9-05ed-4aa6-9af9-e97888a11735",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Que peut-on en déduire~?",
        "html": "<p>Que peut-on en déduire ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2c99924e-2855-4c61-9023-9be3560b67ee",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\frac11-\\frac13+\\frac15 - \\dots = \\frac\\pi4$ et $\\frac11-\\frac12+\\frac13-\\dots=\\ln 2$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac11-\\frac13+\\frac15 - \\dots =\n\\frac\\pi4\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac11-\\frac12+\\frac13-\\dots=\\ln 2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
